sequenceDiagram
    participant U as Usuario
    participant UI as Chat UI
    participant API as /api/chat (Proxy)
    participant GW as Gateway
    participant AI as Gemini + MCPs

    Note over UI: Estado: empty state<br/>Sprite: idle_half_blink

    U->>UI: Escribe pregunta
    UI->>UI: Valida: length ≤ 1000, auth ok
    UI->>UI: Agrega msg user (amber bubble)
    UI->>UI: setLoading(true)

    Note over UI: Sprite header: thinking_squint<br/>Loading: "Buscando información..."

    UI->>API: POST /api/chat {message}

    Note over API: Security checks
    API->>API: 1. Session check ✓
    API->>API: 2. Rate limit ✓
    API->>API: 3. Input validation ✓
    API->>API: 4. Prompt injection check ✓

    API->>GW: POST /api/chat<br/>+ Bearer token<br/>+ X-API-Key
    GW->>AI: Process with Gemini + MCP tools
    AI-->>GW: Response + sources

    GW-->>API: {reply, sources, warnings}
    API-->>UI: JSON response

    UI->>UI: Agrega msg assistant (dark card)
    UI->>UI: setLoading(false)

    Note over UI: Sprite: explaining_talking<br/>Sources badge: 📊 JNE

    alt Error de red
        UI->>UI: Sprite: loading_worried
        UI->>UI: "No se puede conectar"
    end

    alt Rate limit
        API-->>UI: 429
        UI->>UI: "Alcanzaste el límite"
    end

    alt Prompt injection
        API-->>UI: 200 (blocked)
        UI->>UI: "Solo info electoral"
        Note over GW: Gateway NUNCA se enteró<br/>0 tokens gastados
    end
